Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的傢伙們說要交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.25,0:01:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.51,0:01:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到你們那邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好了 別開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.73,0:01:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手放在頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什麼可疑的動作就開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:01:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.74,0:02:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.67,0:02:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是位可以信任的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能想個辦法見到我愛人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果去了 不知道會遇到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在軍部被反布拉德雷派掌握的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能排除
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請再忍耐一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}天之瞳 地之門
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然說不承認真理？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你以為你集合了人柱就贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可沒那麼容易讓你用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡說些沒用的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起來嗎 要逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們可跑不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們已經在我肚子裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大人還是父親就在這裡面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬斯坦古君在父親大人那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是完好無損就不能保證了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆丁女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.23,0:04:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的全身眼球的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是長生不老吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不否認嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾馮斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個歸我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人是辦不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我有鍊丹術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍊丹術確實在鍊金術被封印的時候也能用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小的人造人就交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得真簡單呢 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強制打開了大佐的門？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能用那種方法的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼一直以來沒有幹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:04:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在把我捲入鍊成中的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說了「本不想用這招 不過也是沒辦法」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 對他們來講風險很高嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 能用鍊金術
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來都用黑影子躲開的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又把我家弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻煩的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長生不老
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿下了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不需要妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙能無動作地…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是依然無法和司令部取得聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市內各處伊修瓦爾人出沒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在數個地方和憲兵隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間和你們說明了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命 救命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們什麼都不做 請告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個家是在這個地方沒錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越來越黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伙進展順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣直面死亡真是不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純粹地只有一直戰鬥到死的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:07:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經歷 出生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人種 性別 名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不被任何東西所束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不為任何人 只是戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情是多麼暢快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到達了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.92,0:08:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的全力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管來毀滅我試試
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無名之人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信 你臉上是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然會用這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到前段時間為止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:09:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己都無法想像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在考慮自己能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後想到的是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我兄長的研究書中得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再構築的鍊成陣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要掙扎到什麼程度 人類
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去幫梅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普萊德怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜點 霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾馮斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊很溫和嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在完成你的使命之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓我活下去？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就在這之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你們打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你個子小
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直與比自己高大的人戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:11:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與比自己小的對手戰鬥的經驗很少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 如果打到你就抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的確一直和大個子戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才知道小個子的攻擊模式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有動作也能鍊成真是麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該工作了 各位人柱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點去鍊成陣的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我帶到中心去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被吞噬的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有把這個星球想像成一個生命體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 比起生命也許該說是系統
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你們人類一個人的情報量完全無法比擬的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶龐大的宇宙情報系統
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果打開了那扇門
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底能得到多強大的力量呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:14:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們想過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在使用各位人柱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開這道門
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中心在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的中心是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把世界弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的兒子古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是從我這裡出生的強欲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是你想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.78,0:16:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門之間相互戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.95,0:18:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕妙的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我壓制這股能量就已經用盡全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用這個力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來打開這個星球的門
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.73,0:19:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.79,0:20:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比拿可 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,0:20:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打你一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛…德…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回應我的靈魂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.92,0:21:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.98,0:22:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不會再被你束縛了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.44,0:22:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你拉下地面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.04,0:22:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為我身體的一部分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.12,0:24:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類啊 拜倒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.04,0:24:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將其稱作神的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.56,0:24:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.25,0:24:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不承認就戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.76,0:24:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賭上你們的榮耀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.17,0:24:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 鋼之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.75,0:24:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.45,0:24:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第61話 吞噬神之人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.60,0:24:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.54,0:24:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無依無靠之人所製造的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.88,0:00:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.22,0:00:08.11,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}終於找到了  全新的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:12.21,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}日月卻來礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.39,0:00:17.64,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}我前往的地方  不是「未來」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.64,0:00:21.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}僅僅不停地追趕著「過去」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:27.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}不停地鳴響著 那過去的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:32.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}彷彿無法原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.33,0:00:37.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}差不多了吧  那厭倦搜索的臉龐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.86,0:00:42.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}丟掉心裡的糾結
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:47.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}雨  總有會停的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:53.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}這麼漫長  卻如此冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:58.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}雨  為什麼會選擇我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:03.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}籠罩著我  真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.07,0:01:07.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}雨  已經忘了停
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:13.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}今天依然持續下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:18.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}在默默撐開的雨傘下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:29.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}接近那溫暖的懷抱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.88,0:00:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.25,0:22:42.79,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur2}從那天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.79,0:22:47.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}就決定不再哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:52.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur2}即使承擔再多的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.61,0:22:57.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}仍有無法原諒的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.20,0:23:01.21,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已經無法回到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.21,0:23:03.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那平凡的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:08.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我還沒有做成任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.75,0:23:14.01,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你的記憶之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.01,0:23:19.87,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}又有一塊  消逝而去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.55,0:23:22.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回望今日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.89,0:23:25.63,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想變得更堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:30.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}期望這個聲音總有一天可以傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.78,0:23:33.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.14,0:23:35.88,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在風停止的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.88,0:23:40.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}仰望天空追尋著你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.33,0:23:47.92,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}在黎明前散發的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.08,0:23:53.47,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}將會變成彩虹
